{#
Newsletter template.

Generates a newsletter email with:
- Subject line
- Preview text
- Main content sections
- Footer with links

Required context:
- title: Newsletter title
- summary: Object with short, medium, long summaries
- tags: Object with categories and keywords

Optional context:
- highlights: List of highlight objects
- chapters: List of chapter objects
- author: Author name
- subscribe_link: Newsletter subscribe link
- unsubscribe_link: Unsubscribe link
- website_link: Main website link
#}
